title: Human Universe (2014) [720p][Bluray]
description:
Thanks to tlacatlc6 for providing and ripping the Bluray.

Brian travels the globe to discuss these topics with examples from our planet and others in the universe.

Season 1

Apeman Spaceman S1, Ep1
Brian Cox charts our story from apes to the birth of civilization and then to the stars.
 
Why Are We Here? S1, Ep2
Brian Cox tackles the question that unites the 7 billion people on Earth, why are we here?
 
Are We Alone? S1, Ep3
In a galaxy with over 200 billion star systems, Brian Cox ask the question - are we alone?
 
A Place in Space and Time S1, Ep4
Brian Cox looks at how we came to understand we are not at the centre of the universe.
 
What Is Our Future? S1, Ep5
Brian concludes his exploration by asking, what next for the ape that went to space?
